<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About McKenzie Towne</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">McKenzie Towne homes have the nostalgic feeling of those in a small town and the community takes rigorous steps to ensure that feeling, including naming the community centre McKenzie Town Hall. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is separated into four areas: Inverness, Elgin, Prestwick and High Street, each with different architecture which give off the feeling of European style. Luscious ponds and green spaces characterize the community as an eco-community.</p>
        </div>
